PrecisRe-appointment of GIRARD LANDRY, of Trois-Rivières-Ouest, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Quebec Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of eighteen months, effective July 6, 2001.
